demand_matrix_12x12

Transaction matrix (rev. 2013) This matrix contains the production of the chilean economy divided into 12 industries. The measuring unit is CLP million of the year 2013

wage_demand_matrix

Wage and demand matrix (rev. 2008) This matrix contains the wage, intermediate demand and disaggregated final demand of the chilean economy divided into 12 industries. The final demand is given by components (household consumption, government consumption, etc.) and aggregated. The measuring unit is CLP million of the year 2013.
